local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["halibut"]={"halibut","['hælɪbət]","['hælɪbət]","n.大比目鱼",'n.大比目鱼','||Halibut|| are demersal fish which live in the North Pacific and the North Atlantic oceans. They are highly regarded food fish.','大比目鱼是生活在北太平洋和大西洋的底栖鱼；他们是被高度重视的食用鱼。','a fatty oil from halibut livers that is used as a source of vitamin A.','从大比目鱼的肝脏中提取的脂油,用作维他命a的来源。'}
